# Track this repo's Claude Code project skills, overriding the user-global
# ~/.gitignore_global rule that drops all of .claude/. Order matters: un-ignore
# the dir so git descends into it, re-ignore its contents (keeps goal.json etc.
# out), then allow only .claude/skills/ back in.
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
